ch details can be considered otherwise foregone conclusions, given the fact that the spell's effect is to alter properties, traditionally the province of transmutation, and its clear similarities with [[glassteel (spell)]] in 1st and 2nd edition.<br>Furthermore, Boyd explicitly states his intent to recreate ''glassteel'', further confirming that the spell is intended to behave similarly to ''glassteel''. Thus, this information is accepted, with this note added to explain at length the caveat that it is unpublished material.
