'''''Trobriand's glassteel''''' was a spell that hardened materialsThough no mention is made of the spell rendering the substance clearer, chalcedony is translucid at best, not transparent in nature; the ''Vanrakdoom'' examples are explicitly transparent. It is assumed in this article that the spell modifying the look of chalcedony is more likely than a naturally transparent chalcedony. It was akin to ''[[glassteel (spell)|glassteel]]''.
